@startuml
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam nodesep 50
node "Client (Navigateur)" as Client
node "Vercel - Frontend" as Vercel
node "Render - Backend (Node.js)" as Render
database "MongoDB Atlas" as MongoDB
cloud "Cloudinary (images)" as Cloudinary

Client --> Vercel : HTTP(S) requests (UI)
Vercel --> Render : API requests (HTTP(S))
Render --> MongoDB : MongoDB connection (MONGO_URI)
Render --> Cloudinary : Upload / retrieve images

note left of Render
Backend déployé sur Render
Node.js + Express
Gestion des uploads -> Cloudinary
Connexion DB -> MongoDB Atlas
end note

note right of Vercel
Frontend React déployé sur Vercel
Communique via l'API publique
end note

@enduml
